    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine Domini nostri Iehsu Christi dei eterni, anno ab incarnatione
                        eius millesimo centesimo trigesimo sexto, septimo kalendas martii,
                        indictione tertiadecima. Sancta autem et venerabilis <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesia</rs> et <rs key="#Hospitals">ospitali</rs> deo et <orgName
                            key="#Churches #Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206">beati Sancti
                            Gilii</orgName> quod est fondatum et edificatum in loco qui vocatur
                            <placeName ref="#places/3207" key="#Churches #Hospitals"
                            >Altepasscio</placeName>. Ego quidem <persName ref="#people/3219"
                            >Samirella</persName> que olim fui iugalis <persName><name
                                ref="Lucterius">Lucterii</name></persName>, filii quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Robertus">Roberti</name></persName> et modo sum
                        iugalis <persName ref="#people/3213">Bonifatii</persName> filii quondam
                            <persName ref="#people/3216">Sexmondi</persName> (…)
                            <ref>interrogata</ref> a duobus germanis meis (…) dixi quod (…) per meam
                        bonam voluntatem facio (…). Comuniter nos, ego et <persName><name
                                ref="Bernarduccius">Bernarduccius</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Wizo">Guittoni</name></persName> filius in vice
                        suprascripti Lucterii per hanc cartulam pro anime mee remedio et pro remedio
                        anime predicti Lucterii offerimus tibi Deo et iam dicte ecclesie et ospitali
                        videlicet integram unam <rs key="#Petiae">petiam</rs> de terra illa que est
                        posita in loco qui vocatur <placeName ref="#places/3209" key="#Petiae"
                            >Cafagio</placeName>, que tenet unum caput in terra <persName><name
                                ref="Wilgia">Guilgie</name></persName> filie quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Rodelandus">Rolandi</name></persName>, aliut caput tenet in
                        terra <persName><name ref="Pandulfinus">Pandolfini</name></persName> filii
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Favilla">Faville</name></persName>, latum unum
                        tenet in terra <persName><name ref="Armanectus">Armanecti</name></persName>
                        filii quondam <persName><name ref="Rodelandus">Rolandi</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Ildebrandus">Ildebrandi</name></persName> filii
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Cantinus">Cantini</name></persName>, aliut
                        latus tenet in terra de suprascripto ospitale. <ref>Pena in duplum.
                            Maledizioni.</ref> Actum in loco qui vocatur <placeName
                            ref="#places/3210">Puzostorli</placeName>. Singna manuum suprascripte
                        Samirelle et Bernarduccii, qui hancartulam (sic) fieri rogaverunt. Singna
                        manuum <persName><name ref="Rainuccius">Ranuccini</name></persName> filii
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Gisla">Gislle</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Hugo">Uchionis</name></persName> filii quondam
                        *** qui predicta Samirella interrogaverunt. Singna manuum <persName><name
                                ref="Merollare">Merollari</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Garilius">Garilgiani</name></persName> germani filiorum quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petris</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Meraviglioso de Lucca"
                            >Meravilgiosi</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            >Lucca</placeName> et <persName><name ref="Petrus"
                            >Petri</name></persName> filii <persName><name ref="Mencuccius Capectus"
                                >Mencuccii Capechii</name></persName> rogatorum <rs key="#Witness"
                            >testium</rs>. (S) <persName><name ref="Hubertus"
                            >Ubertus</name></persName> donni inperatoris <rs key="#Notary"
                            >notarium</rs> post traditam complevi et dedi.</ab>
                </div>
